{"tid":1939502,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"David Webb首季賬面計蝕逾1.8億；但同時表示「一些股票估值變得吸引，我正在增持」。","createTime":"2020-03-23T07:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T11:24:56.000Z","uid":134993,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"327340607eb617bd9d40ec36d2eeaa1f180692d9","tid":1939502,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"Webb認為，各地封城鎖國有一定效用，預期相關疫情不會長達數個月；屆時，疫情受控的經濟體自然恢復活動及互相往來。基於以上多個因素，Webb估計，現時相當接近全球恐慌的高峯期，一旦投資者意識到最恐慌階段已過，股市便會開始反彈，隨時在兩周內出現。<br />\n<br />\nWebb坦言，無從預計哪一個時刻見底，「但一些股票的估值變得吸引，我正在增持」。Webb正在留意的股票類別和行業相當廣泛，他指如果相信某些股票的商業模式，到時可能就是增持時機，毋須參考大市整體市賬率，但他拒絕評論任何個股或行業。"},{"pid":"0fc0d2d9c2f63efa013afa8fa85f9f3a80118820","tid":1939502,"uid":208376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"支那楠哥:free cash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09032950efe080f9f4bd6ddd81ccd8abf574d796","tid":1939502,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"連燈仔： webb哥都要散貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c13c4c0cb0782bab198780a465f008821027080","tid":1939502,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"輸咁多重有本?你老母。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8964679104b2d5b94a9359e5f22fc03b05a98516","tid":1939502,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2442c47415e420a63d5b003a64f86f71b43eb393","tid":1939502,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi